title.narrative: Contract with Imperial Health Sciences for receiving, warehousing and distributing drugs

description.narrative: This activity (Contract with Imperial Health Sciences for receiving, warehousing and distributing drugs) is a component of Malawi Health Sector Support Programme reported by FCDO, with a funding type of 'Procurement of Services' and a budget of £5,656,961. This component benefits Malawi, and works in the following sector(s): Basic health care. , with the following implementing partners: Deloitte, Imperial Health Sciences, Oxford Policy Management. The start date is 24-03-2014 and the end date is 31-12-2016.
